criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Participants who are Singapore citizens or Singapore Permanent Residents, and plan to
             be followed up throughout pregnancy and intend to deliver at KKH;

          2. Aged 21 and above;

          3. Singleton pregnancy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Have serious skin conditions (e.g. eczema) that precludes wearing the sensor for 14
             days;

          2. Patients who have any other chronic disease such as chronic kidney disease.

          3. Unable to read or speak English
